Package: com.cytroll.app
Name: Cytroll
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Maintainer: Cytroll Team <cytroll@local>
Depends: firmware (>= 15.0), ellekit
Description: Rootless package manager and bootstrap manager for TrollStore.
 Cytroll installs a Procursus environment into /var/jb and provides
 native APT/dpkg management without modifying the signed system volume.
Section: Applications
Priority: optional
